Info Data: The Modern Education Society's Wadia College of Engineering (MESWCOE), Pune was established in 1999. The college is affiliated to Savitribai Phule Pune University, Pune and is approved by AICTE, New Delhi and sanctioned by Government of Maharashtra. MESWCOE offers a 4-year full-time B.Tech. course in three specializations and a 2-year full-time M.Tech. course in three specializations at UG and PG levels.

College Name: Modern Institute of Engineering and Technology - [MIET]
Info Data: Modern Institute of Engineering and Technology (MIET), Hooghly was established in 2010 by Badal Deb Memorial Educational Foundation to propagate high quality Technical education and to participate in the noble nation building process with the Indian youngsters.

College Name: Neotia Institute of Technology Management and Science - [NITMAS]
Info Data: Neotia Institute of Technology Management and Science (NITMAS), Kolkata was established in the year 2008. It is formerly known as Institute of Technology and Marine Engineering.  NITMAS is a dynamic endeavour of The Ambuja Neotia Group in the field of technological education. NITMAS is committed to the pursuit of excellence and to attain holistic development for all students. By providing a truly inspirational academic environment, the institute ensures that its students emerge as responsible citizens with a strong allegiance to collective advancement.

Prakasam Engineering College (PEC) was established in 2001. It is sponsored by the Amma Education Society. The members of the foundation are eminent personalities in various walks of life such as education, research, industry, business and administration.

College Name: Prince Shri Venkateshwara Padmavathy Engineering College - [PSVPEC]
Info Data: The main aim of Prince Shri Venkateshwara Padmavathy Engineering College is to meet the challenges and demand of the highly advanced scientific and technological fields and to prepare to meet the man power needs of the world. Mission of the college is to provide goal-oriented, quality-based and value-added education through state-of-the-art technology on a par with international standards.

College Name: QIS College of Engineering and Technology - [QISCET]
Info Data: The Engineering Programs offered at QIS College of Engineering and Technology are designed for career initiation and growth in the competitive market place. There is equal emphasis on theoretical concepts as well as practical insights, making our programs the right weapons to conquer the career goals. Mission of the college is to impart quality education by continuous development of infrastructure and to provide the state-of-the-art equipment/software.

RK College of Engineering, established in 2008, is approved by AICTE and affiliated to JNTUK. RK College of Engineering is a Hi-tech modern engineering college situated in Vijayawada Andhra Pradesh. The college is known to provide high-quality education to the young minds and shape them excellently and dynamically. While focusing on the academic excellence of the students the college also aims in providing skills and overall development to the students by involving them in various co-curricular activities.

Rajiv Gandhi Institute of Technology is situated in Mumbai and offers undergraduate course in 5 disciplines viz computer science, electronics and telecom, information technology, instrumentation engineering and mechanical engineering. The college is affiliated to University of Mumbai and is accredited by AICTE. The institute has been awarded "A" grade by the government of Maharashtra.

SVS College of Engineering (SVSCE), Coimbatore was established in 2009 under Velammal Subbiah Educational Trust. It is affiliated to Anna University of Technology, Coimbatore and approved by All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE), New Delhi. It is an ISO 9001:2008 Certified institute. The vision of the college is to promote character and value based education in the minds of younger generation and to empower excellence in providing education in the standard of the globe. The mission of the college is to impart high quality technical education and par with international standards through state of art infrastructure, highly qualified and competent faculty and to develop knowledge and skills of students to face the challenges across the globe with confidence and ease.

Sasi Institute Of Technology & Engineering is running under Sasi Educational Society. The institute was established in the year 2002 in the Business hub of West Godavari district, Tadepalligudem town and is well connected to both road & rail transport.

College Name: Shivajirao S Jondhale College of Engineering - [SSJCE]
Info Data: Shivajirao S. Jondhale College of Engineering (SSJCOE), Thane was established in 1994 by Samarth Samaj. This engineering college is one of the esteemed institutions of S. H. Jondhale educational complex and it is named as Shivajirao S. Jondhale College of Engineering.The college arranges workshops in the areas like stress management, time management, interpersonal skill, communication skill, interview skills, which benefit the students.

Shree Devi Institute of Technology (SDIT), Mangalore was established in 2006.Aim of the Institute is to provide students with a rich and intense learning environment so that they acquire the knowledge and skills needed for succeeding in their professional as well as personal lives.

Sinhgad Academy of Engineering - SAE Pune was established in the year 2005. Sinhgad Academy of Engineering is a technical education institute in the city of Kondhwa, Pune, India. The institute is managed by the Sinhgad Technical Education Society (STES).

College Name: Sir Visvesvaraya Institute Of Technology - [SVIT] Chincholi
Sree Dattha Institute of Engineering and Science - [SDES]
Info Data: Sree Dattha Institute of Engineering and Science (SDES), Rangareddi is one of the premier Engineering Colleges in Telangana. The institute comes under the aegis of Sree Dattha Group of Institutions. The institute is ranked 19th at State Level by Times of India.  SDES offers 5 Undergraduate Programs, 6 Postgraduate Programs, 5 Diploma Programs and MBA in the discipline of Computer Science, Electrical & Electronics, Electronics & Communication, Civil Engineering and Mechanical Engineering. Admission is done through national and state entrance exams. The institute has 2 sister colleges which are as follows:

College Name: Sri Vijaya Vittala Institute of Technology- [VVIT]
Info Data: Sri Vijaya Vittala Institute of Technology (VVIT), Bangalore was established in 2008 under Sri Vijaya Vittala Charitable and Educational Trust. Trust has been engaged in the noble task of providing opportunity to the youth in acquiring higher technical education thus making a significant contribution in providing a strong intellectual base, balanced personality and foundation for the education of the youth hence contributing to the productivity and growth of the nation.

The St. Joseph Engineering College is a private college recognised by AICTE, New Delhi has been established in the year 2002. The college is affiliated to Visvesvaraya Technological University, Belgaum, Karnataka State. The college is NBA accredited. The college has a great campus spread across 35 acres.

Swami Vivekanand College of Engineering (SVCE), Indore was established in 2004 under Swami Vivekanand Group of Institutions. It is affiliated to Rajiv Gandhi Proudyogiki Vishwavidyalaya (RGPV), Bhopal. It is approved by All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE), New Delhi and recognised by Directorate of Technical Education (DTE), Madhya Pradesh. It is an ISO 9001:2008 Certified Institute. The institute is spread on 25 acre of land and located on Indore-Khandwa highway no. SH-27, about 16 km from Indore Railway Station and about 10 km away from Devi Ahilya Vishwavidyalaya (DAV) campus at Bhawarkuan, Indore.

Syed Ammal Engineering College, a self-financing institution, is one among the several educational institutions founded by Late. Dr. E.M. Abdullah. It was established in 1998. It aims to achieve Academic excellence in technical education and to produce Disciplined and Qualitative engineers and technologists to fulfill the expectation of the society. It offers six under graduate and five post graduate courses in the field of engineering and technology. It also offers management programmes. It is located at Ramanathapuram, Tamil Nadu.

Tripura Institute of Technology (TIT), earlier known as Polytechnic Institute. It was started with conventional branches of Civil, Electrical and Mechanical Engineering. In 1995, Electronics & Tele-Communication Engineering was introduced. Now, the college offers 5 Bachelor Degree in (Civil Engineering, Computer Science & Engineering, Electronics & Tele-Communication Engineering, Mechanical Engineering and Electrical Engineering) and 8 Diploma courses (Automobile Engineering, Civil Engineering, Computer Science & Technology, Electrical Engineering, Electronics & Tele-Communication Engineering, Food Processing Technology, Mechanical Engineering and Architectural Assistantship).

Yagyavalkya Institute of Technology (VIT), a premier engineering college of Pink city of Rajasthan was established in 2003 having drawn inspiration from Maharishi Yagyavalkya. It has highly qualified, experienced and dedicated faculty members of international repute who have been instrumental in realizing the dream of providing world class technical education. It is situated in Sitapura, Jaipur, Rajasthan. It offers five undergraduate and five post graduate courses in field of Engineering.

College Name: Gojan School of Business and Technology - [GSBT]
Info Data: Gojan School of Business and Technology (GSBT) was established in 2005. It is run by Gojan Educational Trust, Chennai with great ideal and vision to achieve far reaching results in the service of Education. It is located Redhils, Chennai. GSBT provides innovative educational and training modules to eligible men and women students. It offers seven undergraduate and six postgraduate courses in the field of engineering and technology. It also offers management programmes.

CMR Institute of Technology was established in 2005 under the aegis of the CMR Group of Institutions. It is one of the three colleges established by MGR Educational Society. CMRIT is a UGC Autonomous College, approved by the AICTE and accredited by NAAC with an ‘A’ grade and is also NBA accredited. It is affiliated to Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University Hyderabad. CMR Institute of Technology is also ranked at the 18th position under “Top Emerging Private Engineering Colleges” Category in India and 18th among the “Top Private Engineering Colleges” category in Telangana by The Week.

PET Engineering College, Thanjavur was established by Popular Educational Trust in September 28, 1998. The trust came into existence in 1996 and is completely devoted to imparting world class technical education to youth of the country. It is situated at a 57 acre area on Vallioor – Tiruchendur Highway, 3 Km from the town of Vallioor. Its nearest Railway station Vallioor is 3km away.

College Name: Patel College of Science and Technology - [PCST]
Info Data: Patel College of Science and Technology (PCST) was established in the year 2002 and situated in city Indore, State of Madhya Pradesh. It is manage by Vanshpati Smriti Shikhsa Samiti and known for its high quality technical education, state of art laboratories, high profile faculties and for the environment conducive for extracting the potential of each student. The Training & Placement Cell is guided by a Faculty Advisory Committee and supported by Student Placement Committee.

Usha Mittal Institute of Technology - [UMIT] is a very reputable academic institution working towards transforming the lives of women. The institute empowers young women by providing them engineering education of the top most quality. The institute aims at achieving good excellence in rendering young women with engineering education and establishing good connections with international and national organizations in pursuing academic excellence. The institute fosters overall development and progress of women technologists and engineers by the encouragement of interactions and communication in engineering and computing professions.

The Vaageswari College of Engineering was established by the Sree Vaageswari Educational Society. The colleges impart goal oriented, quality based and value added education with state-of-the-art technical and non-technical resources. The Vaageswari Colleges are located at Karimnagar town, on Rajiv Rahadari Highway towards Hyderabad.

Vishveshwarya Institute of Engineering & Technology, under Shrinath Trust was established in the year 2000 to impart quality higher education. The institute runs under Vishveshwarya group of institutions.

NIIT University (NU) is a not for profit UGC (University Grants Commission) approved institution. A premier institution, marked by higher learning and research, NU seeks to create original thinkers who will lead the knowledge society of the future. The University offers 4-year programs in B.Tech. (Computer Science & Engineering, Electronics & Communication, Biotechnology, Data Science, and Cyber Security), 4-year Integrated MBA (Marketing & Marketing Analytics, Entrepreneurship, Finance Banking & FinTech, Business Analytics, Communication & Media studies, Digital & Social Media Marketing), 4-year Integrated M.Sc (Computer Science) and 3-year BBA (Finance, Banking & Insurance, Digital Marketing, Business Analytics, Family Managed Business). Post Graduate Diploma in Technology Risk Management (PGDTRM) offered by NIIT University along with its partner Global Risk Management Institute (GRMI) is a full time 6 months on-campus program followed by 6 months of Hands-On aid Internship, making it 1-year full-time specialized program.

CT Group of Institutions, Jalandhar, Punjab; was established in 1997, affiliated to I.K.Gujral Punjab Technical University (IKGPTU), Jalandhar, with a vision to produce leaders, achievers and winners for the global corporate world. It wishes to provide novel vistas of opportunities for the students by understanding their requirements and accordingly catering a worthwhile education. The college is committed to providing an ever-improving educational system by bringing changes in the delivery of the education and designing an atmosphere which ensures employability for the students. The group targets continuously trying to bring in the best educational system. It is dedicated and committed to the pursuit of excellence. It strives to prepare the students for the leadership role in the multifaceted world. It provides a bunch of educational institutions from the pre-school to postgraduate level; and with a dedicated and veteran staff, conducive environment and excellent infrastructure; it targets to provide an ideal and endowing education that can stand as paramount around the world.

College Name: ABMSP's Anantrao Pawar College of Engineering & Research - [APCOER]
Info Data: ABMS Parishad’s Anantrao Pawar College of Engineering and Research (ABMSPCOER), Pune is the outcome of dedicated and well known educationalists and socially conscious people who empathised with the plight of  less fortunate and oppressed people and spurred into action, establishing a new era of quality and unbiased education which is carried forward today by ABMSPCOER. The noble vision to empower the economically backward section through a system of value-based education, coupled with the mission to produce graduates highly skilled for employability or to be entrepreneurs, nurtures students in all spheres of life. Effectively using engineering knowledge for society’s benefit, ABMSPCOER establishes the right foundations for technical and humane learning.

Institute of Technology & Management (ITM) is a private engineering college located in Aligarh district of Uttar Pradesh. The college is managed by CM Trust Aligarh. The college started functioning in 2008-09. The ITM College is affiliated to Uttar Pradesh Technical University and approved by AICTE, New Delhi

College Name: JCT College of Engineering and Technology
Info Data: JCT College of Engineering and Technology is a part of Jan Nayak Ch.Devi Lal Vidyapeeth. The College is a Self-financing; Non-Autonomous affiliated to renowned university.

JIMS Engineering Management Technical Campus, established in 2013 is affiliated to Guru Gobind Singh Indraprastha University (GGSIPU). The undergraduate level courses are offered in the streams of Engineering, Law, Business Administration, Computer Application, Education, Commerce and Journalism. The courses offered are approved by the All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE), Bar Council of India (BCI), and National Council of Teacher Education (NCTE). The institute provides admission on the basis of IPU CET, CLAT, CUET UG and JEE Main. For admission at JIMS Engineering Management Technical Campus, the candidate must have valid scores in JEE/IPU CET/ CUT and CLAT  followed by university counselling.

Dhanalakshmi Srinivasan College of Engineering (DSCE), Coimbatore is an emerging institute of excellence in Engineering Education located on the East Coast Road, in the Historic Town of Mamallapuram. The college is run by the Srinivasan Charitable and Educational Trust which has been in the field of education for more than a decade. DSCE offers undergraduate and postgraduate programs in the discipline of Engineering and Management.

Vaigai College of Engineering was started by the Vaigai Educational Trust to offer services to the less privileged parts of the country. The objective of Vaigai College of Engineering is to produce top class engineers who have both subject knowledge and working knowledge. It is located in Madurai in Tamil Nadu and offers courses such as B.E. Mechanical Engineering, B.E. Civil Engineering, B.E Electronics and Communication Engineering, B.E Electrical & Electronics Engineering, and B.E Computer Science & Engineering.

Jagannath University, Bahadurgarh was established in 2013 and is located in Bahadurgarh, Haryana. It is a member of Association of Indian Universities. The university is a detailed and well-planned output of a registered non-profitable educational trust named as Jagan Nath Gupta Educational Society. The university has been approved by UGC, AIU, COA, BCI, and NCTE.
The university offers various undergraduate, postgraduate and doctoral courses in various streams. to these courses are conducted every year.
The university’s motto is to develop as a Centre of Excellence in higher education. For this purpose, it focuses on skill development and industry linkage and ensures employability particularly in technical and professional education. It believes in the overall development of its students. The University has MoUs with various corporate and industrial organizations which help its students in securing meaningful jobs in the corporate world.

Established in 2002, the Bhopal Institute of Technology & Science (BITS) is one of the premier engineering colleges in Madhya Pradesh. It is a self-financing college and is approved by AICTE and the Directorate of Technical Education (DTE), Madhya Pradesh.

St. Mary’s Engineering College (SMEC) is a private self-financing institution located in Hyderabad. It was established in 2007 with the noble aim of imparting technical education and skills in rural students. The college is approved by the AICTE and affiliated to JNTUH, Hyderabad. The campus is set in 120 acres of land amidst scenic valleys and hills. SMEC is the only institute in the state of Telangana with the highest budget to nurture entrepreneurship which in turn convert the innovative ideas into products.

Maharishi University of Information Technology (MUIT) is a private university established in 2001 and approved by UGC. It offers undergraduate, diploma and doctoral courses in the discipline of Data Science, Law, Animation and Journalism and Mass Communication. Admission to the courses depends on the performance of the candidates in the entrance examination conducted by the University.

Meerut Institute of Technology is situated in Meerut in the Uttar Pradesh state of India. Established in 2007, it is approved by AICTE and affiliated to APJ Abdul Kalam Technological University. Meerut Institute of Technology provides 8 different courses at the UG level. The institute values the significance of the overall development of personality and to achieve certain skills such as Communication Skills, Negotiation Skills, Critical Reasoning Ability, Right Attitude, Self Image, Motivation, Goals, Resume Writing, Mock Interviews, etc.

College Name: VSB College of Engineering Technical Campus
Info Data: VSB College of Engineering Technical Campus is a private college which was established in 2012. The Institute is located at Coimbatore in Tamil Nadu and is approved by AICTE. The institute is affiliated to Anna University (AU), Chennai. The institute aims to make the students learn new Technologies & Engineering and mould them into future creators, developers, designers, manufacturers and leaders.

Guru Nanak Institutions Technical Campus (GNITC) holds over 19 years of expertise. It was established in the year 2001 and is the only private University in Telangana that has received NAAC A+ from the National Assessment and Accreditation Council. The institute is one of the largest educational groups in India with 10,000+ Students currently enrolled in various programs of studies including Engineering and Technology, Pharmacy, Business Management and Dental Science and was founded by Sri Tavinder Singh Kohli,  visionary industrialist and well-known philanthropist (Founder and Chairman of GNI.)

Bineswar Brahma Engineering College(BBEC), Kokrajhar, Assam was established in 2008 by the Assam state government. The college is approved by All India Council for Technical Education(AICTE), Government of India and Government of Assam.

Rawal institutions is a private institution established in 2008 under the aegis of Goyal Educational and Welfare Society. Rawal institutions include Rawal Institute of Engineering And Technology, Rawal Institute of Management, Rawal College of Education. These Institutions provide quality engineering and management education to students and transform them into employable managers, technocrats, bureaucrats and above all good citizens of India.

Madhyanchal Professional University (MPU), Bhopal was established in 2018 under the aegis of Vanaspati Smriti Shiksha Samiti (VSSS), Bhopal. The Samiti has been promoting a group of 8 colleges at Bhopal and Indore under the banner of Patel Group of Institutions (PGOI). The University provides higher education leading up-to Ph.D. in the disciplines of Science, Education, Humanities, Commerce, Management, Engineering, Medical, Paramedical, Pharmacy, Nursing, Agriculture, Animal Sciences, Forestry, Law, Journalism, Mass Communication, Environment and many other branches.

Yenepoya Institute of Technology (YIT), Mangalore, Karnataka is a private institute providing quality technical education in a few verticals of engineering degree. The college started operating from the year 2008 and is affiliated to Visvesvaraya Technological University (VTU), Belgaum, approved by AICTE India, New Delhi. The institute is located in Moodabidri, Mangalore, Karnataka and spans across 15 acres of lush green land. The institute offers a 4-year degree course in engineering across 5 disciplines. Admissions to this course are entrance-based and admission form along with brochure is available in the institute official website.

Sapkal Knowledge Hub was established in 2005 and approved by AICTE and the Government of Maharashtra. It is a group of educational institutes that provide learning from kindergarten to post-graduation. The institute has been providing education for more than 16 years to 12,000+ students. Sapkal Knowlege Hub has different institutes that offer education in the fields of Pharmacy, Management, and Engineering. Apart from this, it also has an Orchid International School. The institutes under Sapkal Knowlege Hub are affiliated with . Late GN Sapkal College of Engineering and RG Sapkal College of Pharmacy is  The pharmacy institute is also approved by PCI and DTE. It is affiliated with the and .

International School of Engineering (INSOFE), Bangalore, Karnataka is an Applied Engineering school with an area of focus in Data science/ Big data analytics. It is a private institution that won the Education Leadership award in 2017. INSOFE also has branches in Hyderabad and Mumbai. INSOFE provides courses at Certificate, Bachelors, masters and Doctorate level. A well maintained IT-infrastructure is provided that covers all the amenities required by the students.

College Name: Shikshapeeth College of Management and Technology - [SCMT]
Info Data: Shikshapeeth College of Management & Technology (SCMT), New Delhi, affiliated to NAAC “A+” Grade and UGC Approved was established in 2009. This deemed college offers numerous courses at both graduate and postgraduate levels in the field of Technology and Management. It offers a wide range of undergraduate courses like BBA, BCA, B.Tech & Post-Graduate programs like MBA. SCMT also has several national and international tie-ups to impart international standard education exposure to students.

Thakur Institute of Aviation Technology - (TIAT) is a private institute established in 2006 and is located in Kandivali East, Mumbai, Maharashtra. TIAT is among the top AME colleges in India and is the only Institute in India to have 5 approvals from different regulatory authorities. The  Institute is approved by DGCA, New Delhi India. TIAT holds international approvals from EASA, GCAA, BCAA, and CAAB. Further, TIAT provides Practical training commonly referred as Actual Environmental Training (AET) through joint ventures with leading Domestic and International Airlines/Maintenance organizations ensuring students meet the rigorous standards of the aviation industry

BFIT Group of Institutions or BFIT, Dehradun was established by the shadow of Kartar Educational & Cultural Society in 2002 and is affiliated to H.N.B Garhwal Central University. BFIT has 3 campuses in the valley with 5000+ students. The institute offers UG, PG and Diploma Courses in the Disciplines of Science, Humanities, Law, Engineering and Management. The most popular courses of the institute include B.tech, MCA, BA in Journalism and Mass Communication, MBA and BBA courses. Admission is based on the candidate’s performance in the previous qualifying exam.

College Name: AVN Institute of Engineering and Technology - [AVNIET], Ibrahimpatnam
Info Data: AVN Institute of Engineering and Technology is a leading institution destined to offer engineering wisdom and comprehensive prospectus in the pasture of Technological edification. The institution stands with glory to its 27 years of academic brilliance attained by maintaining a balance between scholarly and up to date industrial practices. The vision of the college is to inculcate the fortitude of high target, vigorous mind-set, obedience and multidimensional brilliance in the educatee and endeavor to mould them to reach new statures. The mission of the institution is wisdom through research technique and competence with the global market.

College Name: Amrita Sai Institute of Science and Technology - [ASIST]
Info Data: Amrita Sai Institute of Science & Technology (ASIST), an Autonomous institution affiliated to JNTUK, A.P. and approved by All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE) was established in the year 2007 under the auspices of Amrita Sai Educational Improvement Trust. The institute is also accredited by the NAAC with ‘A’ grade of its quality in technical education. For the last 11 years, the College has tremendously been excelling in all its verticals viz. Engineering, Management, Research, and Development. Sharp focus on quality education, sensible training, and solid research have turned Amrita Sai Institute of Science & Technology into a premier Technical Institution ensuring 100% placement in a wide range of companies.

Arya College of Engineering is amongst the Top Institutes in Rajasthan for Engineering and for Higher Technical Education. ACE Jaipur was founded in the year 2005 and has become the most prominent College in the state as well as the Best Engineering Colleges in Jaipur. All courses at Arya College of Engineering are affiliated to Rajasthan Technical University and approved by AICTE. Check: ACE Jaipur Jaipur Courses and fees

The Bahubali College of Engineering (BCE) is an unaided institution which was established in the year of 1997 and managed by the educational institute S.S.D.J. Jnana Prasaraka Sangha. The main objective of the college is to develop Quality Technical Education System through committed Team Work. It is recognized by the Government of Karnataka. The courses which are offered by the college are Bachelor of Engineering (B.E.) in 5 streams.

Bearys Institute of Technology (BIT), Mangalore was established by the Bearys Group under the aegis of Bearys Academy of Learning, BIT is an institution with a difference. The institute provides outstanding opportunities for higher learning. The institute have a well qualified faculty from across India and abroad, top-of-the-line facilities and a talented student body that will grow in numbers with every passing year.

Bharat Institute of Technology is located in Meerut, Uttar Pradesh and was established in 2001. The institute is accredited by NBA and is affiliated to AKTU, Lucknow. It is one of the top private engineering colleges in the area and comes under the BIT institutions. BIT offers Undergraduate and Postgraduate programmes in fields including Engineering, Pharmaceutical and Management along various specializations. Admissions are based on entrance exam scores. Along with this, BIT is ranked 24th by CSR for the best private engineering college. BIT offers the best infrastructure and academic facilities to help students improve their theoretical as well as practical knowledge.

College Name: Bharati Vidyapeeth College of Engineering - [BVCOE] Navi Mumbai
Info Data: No data found

College Name: Christ College of Engineering and Technology
Info Data: Christ College of Engineering and Technology, Puducherry focuses on creating professionals that are enabled and empowered to compete on international levels based on the knowledge and technical ability. The institution aims to promote freedom of thought and expression in the areas of knowledge and education. CCET strives to achieve educational methods of international standards by an effective Quality Management System and continuously attempting to upgrade the tools of education. On departure from the institute every student should be ethically, psychologically and technically more sound than he or she at the time of joining the institute.

Coorg Institute of Technology was started in the year 1999 under the aegis the Kodava Education Society with an aim of providing quality education to the students of district. College is approved AICTE, New Delhi and is affiliated to Visvervaraya Technological University. College is recognized by Govt. of Karnataka

College Name: Dr. Sivanthi Aditanar College of engineering - [SACOE]
Info Data: Dr. Sivanthi Aditanar College of Engineering (SACOE) was established in 1998 by Padmashri Dr. B. Sivanthi Adityan. It is running under Aditanar Educational Institution. It is a self-financing educational institution situated in Tiruchendur, Tuticorin District. It is offers value added education to empower the student profile.  It is affiliated to Anna University of Technology, Tirunelveli.

College Name: G. Pullaiah College of Engineering and Technology - [GPCET]
Info Data: G. Pullaiah College of Engineering and Technology (GPCET), a well reputed Engineering College in Rayalaseema region was established in 2007 by renowned educationalist Sri G. Pullaiah. It offers BTech courses and it also has an MBA programme. The aim of college is to strive hard in training the students with the current technology and motivate them to take up research problems and innovations. It is located on Kurnool-Nandikotkur High way. The college is approved by the All India Council for Technical Education and affiliated to Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University, Anantapur.

College Name: GSSS Institute of Engineering and Technology for Women - [GSSSIETW]
Info Data: Geetha Shishu Shikshana Sangha Institute of Engineering & Technology for Women is located in Mysore and has been accredited with GRADE “A” by the National Accreditation Assessment Committee (NAAC). GSSSIETW offers 6 B.E Programs in Engineering viz., Electronics and Communication Engineering, Computer Science Engineering, Information Science Engineering, Electrical and Electronics Engineering, Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence and Data Science branches and M. Tech Programs in Digital Communication and Networking, Computer Science Engineering and MBA program, all affiliated to .

College Name: Genba Sopanrao Moze College of Engineering Balewadi
Info Data: Genba Sopanrao Moze College of Engineering was established by Shri. Rambhau Moze in 1999. It is run and managed by Genba Sopanrao Moze Trust, Pune. It seeks to impart quality technical education by a well monitored teaching process and through industry-institute interaction programs.

Guru Nanak Dev Engineering College (GNDEC), Bidar was established in 1980 under Sri Nanak Jhira Saheb Foundation (Trust). Initially, the college was affiliated to Gulbarga University, Gulbarga and in 1998 it got affiliated to Visvesvaraya Technological University (VTU), Belgaum. It is approved by All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE), New Delhi and accredited by National Board of Accreditation (NBA), New Delhi.

Haryana Engineering College owe its existence to a group of professionals dedicated to promote and development of technical education in Haryana under  Mata Sudershan Tilak Raj Dhawan Educational in 1998 with aim to excel in providing qualified engineers.

College Name: Holy Mary Institute of Technology and Science -[HITS]
Info Data: Holy Mary Institute of Technology, Hyderabad was established in 2001.. This distinction was given to HITS-COE in February, 2005 in recognition of its efforts "for identifying the deficiencies of each student at the time of entry and for providing additional inputs by way of extra classes and courses in soft skill development”. HITS College of Engineering is affiliate to J.N.T.U Hyderabad.

ITS Engineering College, Greater Noida is ranked under Top 10 Best Private Engineering Colleges in North India by India Today and awarded Best Engineering College for Industry Interface and Placements in North India by ASSOCHAM. ITS has been ranked by ARIIA (Atal Ranking of Institutions on Innovation Achievements) as the top 6-25 innovative higher education private or self-financed college/ institutions across India and also among the top 3 in Uttar Pradesh. ITS Engineering College, affiliated to Dr. APJ Abdul Kalam Technical University is one of the most advanced engineering colleges in India. With accreditations by NAAC & NBA and approved by AICTE, this institute has a bag full of achievements to boost on.

College Name: ILM College of Engineering and Technology - [ILMCET]
Info Data: ILM College of Engineering & Technology, Ernakulam was established in 2012 under Islamic Learning Mission Trust. It is affiliated to Mahatma Gandhi University, Kottayam and approved by All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE), New Delhi. The College has highly qualified and experienced faculty, well equipped laboratories & workshops and a central library with a large collection of books and journals in all subject areas. The college takes all efforts to groom the students to be more employable by adopting innovative teaching methods, conducting invited lectures, organizing training schemes for development of soft skills, arranging industry-institute interaction programmes etc. It is located at Perumbavoor in Ernakulam district of Kerala.

Indira College of Engineering and Management is ranked 100th in Top Engineering College by Outlook 2019 and ranked 61st in Top 140 Engineering Institutions. The institute comes under the umbrella of Indira Group of Institutes (IGI) Pune. ICEM Pune offers degree courses in the discipline of Engineering and Business Administration.
